originalText.text: I LOVE Carol!!!! I see her in Grand Cayman, and she is the eyebrow Goddess! I get shaping and brows dyed. She gives me the most incredible eyebrows I have ever had. People constantly ask me where I get my brows done so she has a large fan club on the island. So glad I met this woman- she is beautiful, wise and amazing at what she does. You will become a regular once you get your brows done with her. Make sure to book an appointment a few weeks to a month ahead of time- she is very popular!!!

originalText.text: This lady is amazing! We discussed what i wanted for easily an hour, we did templates and Carol had so much patience whilst i picked and adjusted until they were just right. I am over the moon with my eyebrows. It has been around 6 weeks since my 2nd touch up and they look incredible. Initially they do look heavier and she gave me plenty of warning that i should expect them to change whilst healing. All i can say is give it a solid 6-8 week healing period and you will be ecstatic with the results. Truly an artist at her profession, i know where i will be going in the future for all my permanent makeup needs.

originalText.text: LOVE MY SKIN!! I had the Carbon Laser Facial done by Carol and my skin never looked younger and brighter!! I have dull, hyper-pigmented skin and tried different facials but the results never lasted past one day. The Carbon Laser Facial had me GLOWING for weeks!!  Everyone noticed how healthy my skin looked.  It was all one tone - no more blotchy skin!  Carol is super talented and a true expert in her field.   I am getting the eyebrow microblading next!  I wouldn't trust anyone else!

originalText.text:
This beautiful lady with hands of a angel, did my eyebrows.
I had no eyebrows due to over plucking, when I was young.
Plus about 4 years a went through radiation.
I was left with little bit of hair.
So I decide to do this new microblading that every one was talking about.
I did my homework and browse through google.
And guess what a found this amazing lady by the name Carol Furey.
This angel gave me.....my smile back. ...
With her amazing art and delicate hands of angel.
Today I can smile and feel good,when I look at the mirror and see my beautiful eyebrows.
Thank you
Carol Furey.
Tons of hugs and kisses.
May God continue blessing you.

originalText.text:
OMG!!! Carol is AMAZING!! I love her!!!! She is extremely proffesional and super Sweet. She definetely works wonders and miracles. I have been struggling with my brows for soooo long. I would not leave my house without drawing them, I had a hard time going to the beach and pool due to fear of the color smugding (Can you imagine) and yes it has happened (YIKESSS) Now I could sing (I woke up like this) my brows are perfect.

I would 3D Tattoo them a million times more. It is so soo sooo worth it!!! I know there is no perfection in life, but my brows are PERFECT!!!!!!! It looks sooo natural. No one even thinks it's a tattoo..

So if are struggling with your brows search no more!! You have to make an appointment with Carol!!

Wonderful!! :-)

Gracias Carol. Eres magnifica
